Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.71,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord3.375\shad2.7\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs74.25}{\i1}{\i0}‫♪ ...קוארואה! ♪
